{
  "texts": [
    "Participants who failed at least one of two attention checks were excluded from the analyses (n = 29).",
    "The 471 participants in the final sample were 36.2 ± 12.5 (mean ± std) years old and 48% of them identified as female.",
    "All materials and outcome measures were the same as in Study 1a (see Fig.",
    "S2 for distribution of outcome variables).",
    "Unlike Study 1a, however, participants were randomly assigned to one of three experimental conditions."
  ]
}